description.p:
According to a fourth embodiment of the present invention a method of making an article having a metal coating deposited on a substrate is provided which method enhances and promotes the adhesion of the metal coating, preferably a reflective metal coating, to the substrate like a highly smooth or polished glass or plastic. This method comprises: providing a substrate;



    

contacting a surface of said substrate with a solution comprising a Bi metal ion at basic pH, optionally in combination with ammoniacal silver ions; and

applying a metal coating on said activated surface of said substrate.
